{"tid":2130403,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"體院入住宿舍全職運動員及教練今晚至下月4日不能離開","createTime":"2020-07-29T07:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T07:39:33.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b476e8c861dc7df1206f73f9cf89683c8caca6","tid":2130403,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540557-20200729.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540557-20200729.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6YeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=5653e804\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540557-20200729.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f3d5c4b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540557-20200729.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港體育學院今日起實施特別防疫措施，今晚8時起入住體院宿舍的全職運動員和教練，至下月4日晚上8時期間，不能離開。體院餐廳亦只為運動員及教練團隊提供膳食服務，每張餐桌同一時間限一名運動員使用。<br />\n<br />\n體院表示，選擇在這期間不入住體院宿舍的運動員及教練團隊，需要在今晚8時前離開，直至下月4日期間不能再進入體院。<br />\n<br />\n體院各部門將採取特別工作安排，部門主管將按工作需要，讓部分員工在家工作，直至另行通知。"},{"pid":"1c083fb236d859058d72e1a5f3157f34c8c589a5","tid":2130403,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"瘋狂pappaaoapa<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}